## 📖 内容说明 / Content Notice

本项目提供的教材目录与正版教材同步，教材内容版权归原出版社所有。
本项目仅提供教材目录索引和检索工具，不包含任何教材正文内容。

The textbook catalog in this project is synchronized with official textbooks.
All textbook content copyrights belong to their respective publishers.
This project provides only a catalog index and search tools, without any textbook body content.

---

## 🌍 开放公益声明 / Open Public Benefit Statement

本项目是一个开放、公益的代码库，旨在：
- 让更多人便捷地发现和访问中国K12教材资源
- 为海外华人学子学习中文教材提供便利
- 促进教育资源的信息化与开放获取

This is an open-source, public-benefit project that aims to:
- Help people easily discover and access Chinese K-12 textbook resources
- Provide convenience for overseas Chinese students learning Chinese textbooks
- Promote the informatization and open access of educational resources
